text: Chet Phillips (October 23, 1913 - October 7, 1988) was an American gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:1988 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Philadelphia
